    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The behaviour can be really different as soon as we have `null` on some facet values. Some blocks might be displayed when there is actually nothing in it.\nAnd it is actually a bug since some are using `nbHits` (`price-ranges`, `toggle`), and others are using `facetValues.length` (`refinement-list`, `menu`, `hierarchical-menu`), meaning that they don't behave consistently when there are `null` values.\n",
    "created_at": "2015-11-02T14:22:58Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/394#issuecomment-153029874",
    "id": 153029874,
